<lb n="0313b21"/><head type="no">No. 955</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0313b22"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0313007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第五帖，（瑜伽翳迦訖沙囉烏瑟尼沙斫訖囉真言安怛陀那儀則）二十二字＋一【三】＊，（瑜伽翳訖沙囉烏瑟尼沙斫囉真言安怛陀那儀則）二十一字＋一【甲】</note><note n="0313007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第五帖，（瑜伽翳迦訖沙囉烏瑟尼沙斫訖囉真言安怛陀那儀則）二十二字＋一【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊，（瑜伽翳訖沙囉烏瑟尼沙斫囉真言安怛陀那儀則）二十一字＋一【甲】</note><app n="0313007"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">瑜伽翳迦訖沙囉烏瑟尼沙斫訖囉真言安怛陀那儀則一</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">瑜伽翳訖沙囉烏瑟尼沙斫囉真言安怛陀那儀則一</rdg></app><note n="0313007" place="foot" type="rest">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第五帖</note>字頂輪王瑜伽<note n="0313008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">觀行儀軌＝經【三】【甲】</note><note n="0313008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">觀行儀軌＝經【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0313008"><lem>觀行儀軌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">經</rdg></app><note n="0313009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0313009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一卷〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0313009"><lem>一
<lb n="0313b23"/>卷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0313b24"/>
<lb n="0313b25"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0313010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（開府…門）四十一字＝（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智）十一字【宋】【元】【甲】，（唐大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智）十二字【明】</note><note n="0313010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…門）四十一字＝（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智）十一字【宋】【元】【甲】，＝（唐大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智）十二字【明】</note><app n="0313010" word-count="41"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿
<lb n="0313b26"/>肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司
<lb n="0313b27"/>空謚大鑒正號大廣智大興善
<lb n="0313b28"/>寺三藏沙門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">唐大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg></app>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0313b29"/><p>真言行者若求安怛陀<note n="0313011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娜＝那【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0313011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娜＝那【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0313011"><lem>娜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">那</rdg></app>。應作是念。<note n="0313012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我云何＝云何我【三】，云我何【甲】</note><note n="0313012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我云何＝云何我【宋】【元】【明】，＝云我何【甲】</note><app n="0313012"><lem>我云
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0955.0313c" n="0313c"/>
<lb n="0313c01"/>何</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">云何我</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">云我何</rdg></app>能速取成就。當習是三摩地。所謂一切法
<lb n="0313c02"/>無色。猶如虛空性自成就。作如是勝解。當如
<lb n="0313c03"/>本教淨<note n="0313013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">治＝持【三】【甲】</note><note n="0313013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">治＝持【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0313013"><lem>治</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">持</rdg></app>地等。作是三摩地</p>
<lb n="0313c04"/><lg><l>普遍三千界</l><l>充滿智成水</l>
<lb n="0313c05"/><l>有大寶蓮華</l><l>開敷在水中</l>
<lb n="0313c06"/><l>寶莖如須彌</l><l>上方珠網覆</l>
<lb n="0313c07"/><l><note n="0313014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">花＝蓮【三】【甲】</note><note n="0313014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">花＝蓮【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0313014"><lem>花</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">蓮</rdg></app>上有大寶</l><l>八柱以莊嚴</l>
<lb n="0313c08"/><l>想成寶樓閣</l><l>四門當四方</l>
<lb n="0313c09"/><l>珠網蓮鐸等</l><l>及妙拂莊嚴</l>
<lb n="0313c10"/><l>半滿月珠瓔</l><l>垂寶間錯帶</l>
<lb n="0313c11"/><l>是大寶樓閣</l><l>遍滿於有頂</l>
<lb n="0313c12"/><l>應隨力思惟</l><l>觀供養雲海</l>
<lb n="0313c13"/><l>先所觀樓中</l><l>有悅意白繖</l>
<lb n="0313c14"/><l>以眾寶端<note n="0313015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飾＝嚴【三】【甲】</note><note n="0313015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飾＝嚴【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0313015"><lem>飾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">嚴</rdg></app></l><l>寶瓔半滿月</l>
<lb n="0313c15"/><l>妙拂等莊<note n="0313016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚴＝飾【三】【甲】</note><note n="0313016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚴＝飾【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0313016"><lem>嚴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">飾</rdg></app></l><l>繖上有大寶</l>
<lb n="0313c16"/><l>普遍發光<note n="0313017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">明＝相【三】【甲】</note><note n="0313017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">明＝相【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0313017"><lem>明</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">相</rdg></app></l><l>皆散雨眾寶</l>
<lb n="0313c17"/><l>真言智觀行</l><l>於彼樓閣中</l>
<lb n="0313c18"/><l>金剛師子座</l><l>寶蓮華莊嚴</l>
<lb n="0313c19"/><l>珠網蓮繒磬</l><l>白拂等莊嚴</l>
<lb n="0313c20"/><l>一切欲喜樂</l><l>於中圍繞住</l>
<lb n="0313c21"/><l>不遠於身前</l><l>應想第二座</l>
<lb n="0313c22"/><l>一切皆如上</l><l>唯無師子座</l>
<lb n="0313c23"/><l>角門於四處</l><l>嬉戲焚香等</l>
<lb n="0313c24"/><l>次作圓具法</l><l>云何作圓具</l>
<lb n="0313c25"/><l>先應觀諸法</l><l>無性為自性</l>
<lb n="0313c26"/><l>物我同一體</l><l>然後加<note n="0313018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸＝持【甲】</note><app n="0313018"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">持</rdg></app>法</l>
<lb n="0313c27"/><l>云何加諸法</l><l>生老病<note n="0313019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">憂死＝死憂【三】【甲】</note><note n="0313019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">憂死＝死憂【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0313019"><lem>憂死</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">死憂</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0313c28"/><l>攪擾於心田</l><l>如是思惟已</l>
<lb n="0313c29"/><l>應生大悲愍</l><l>由是生智心</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0955.0314a" n="0314a"/>
<lb n="0314a01"/><l>則是光明心<note place="inline">光明<note n="0314001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＋（者）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心＋（者）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314001"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">心者</rdg></app><note n="0314002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即＋（是）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即＋（是）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314002"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">即是</rdg></app>菩提心也</note></l>
<lb n="0314a02"/><l>以大悲熏成</l><l>其體如<note n="0314003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿＝皓【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滿＝皓【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314003"><lem>滿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">皓</rdg></app>月</l>
<lb n="0314a03"/><l>離能取所取</l><l>菩提心已生</l>
<lb n="0314a04"/><l>應住身口意</l><l>所明體加持</l>
<lb n="0314a05"/><l>此名圓具法<note place="inline">即如瑜伽中成身次第也</note></l>
<lb n="0314a06"/><l>族明勝次第<note n="0314004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">知已二字宋元明甲四本俱作夾註</note><note n="0314004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（知已）二字本文＝（知已）二字夾註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314004"><lem>知已</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">知已</note></rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0314005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（知）＋族【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（知）＋族【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314005"><lem>族</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">知族</rdg></app>五部明五部真言也</note></l>
<lb n="0314a07"/><l>眾真言威德<note n="0314006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔知〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔知〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314006"><lem>知</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>已</l>
<lb n="0314a08"/><l>自住部王法<note place="inline">謂一字頂<note n="0314007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輪＋（王法）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輪＋（王法）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314007"><lem>輪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">輪王法</rdg></app>也</note></l>
<lb n="0314a09"/><l>則為當族<note n="0314008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝主【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王＝主【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314008"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">主</rdg></app></l><l>先應印已成<note place="inline">謂大印也</note></l>
<lb n="0314a10"/><l>次明應思惟</l><l>由身口意體</l>
<lb n="0314a11"/><l><note n="0314009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">想＝觀【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">想＝觀【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314009"><lem>想</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">觀</rdg></app>身為諸佛</l><l>於心想月輪</l>
<lb n="0314a12"/><l><note n="0314010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔無垢猶如佛〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔無垢猶如佛〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314010"><lem>無垢猶如佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></l><l>真言者應知</l>
<lb n="0314a13"/><l>有種種光明</l><l>皆從月形生</l>
<lb n="0314a14"/><l>遍至無量界</l><l>復入行人心</l>
<lb n="0314a15"/><l>堅固為五峰</l><l>變為金剛形</l>
<lb n="0314a16"/><l>想在彼<note n="0314011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">掌＝常【甲】</note><app n="0314011"><lem>掌</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">常</rdg></app>中</l><l>復出種種光</l>
<lb n="0314a17"/><l>其光皆遍滿</l><l>至於無邊界</l>
<lb n="0314a18"/><l>而作佛遊戲</l><l>還來瑜岐身</l>
<lb n="0314a19"/><l>如是皆入已</l><l>成普賢大色</l>
<lb n="0314a20"/><l>應觀大菩薩</l><l>諸相皆成就</l>
<lb n="0314a21"/><l>一切莊嚴具</l><l>蓮華鬘灌頂</l>
<lb n="0314a22"/><l>自成摩訶薩</l><l>從瑜岐心生</l>
<lb n="0314a23"/><l>持真言弓箭</l><l>依住於月輪</l>
<lb n="0314a24"/><l>或持鬘而住</l><l>或四方安居</l>
<lb n="0314a25"/><l>隨力觀身前</l><l>諸眾生大樂</l>
<lb n="0314a26"/><l>最上令成就</l><l>一切印嚴手</l>
<lb n="0314a27"/><l>惠施於一切</l><l>諸有情如願</l>
<lb n="0314a28"/><l>并熙怡為舞</l><l>金剛<note n="0314012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬘＝慢【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鬘＝慢【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314012"><lem>鬘</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">慢</rdg></app>流出</l>
<lb n="0314a29"/><l>為左於腰側</l><l>住右作舞勢</l>
<lb n="0314a30"/><l>安立眾生利</l><l>如自明隨形</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0955.0314b" n="0314b"/>
<lb n="0314b01"/><l>諸眾生所<note n="0314013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝思【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝思【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314013"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">思</rdg></app></l><l>皆令成調伏</l>
<lb n="0314b02"/><l>作如是加持</l><l>利益於眾生</l>
<lb n="0314b03"/><l>及餘諸利益</l><l>&CB00256;寫等供養</l>
<lb n="0314b04"/><l>而<note n="0314014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314014"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>陳<note n="0314015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">供養＝奉獻【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">供養＝奉獻【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314015"><lem>供養</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">奉獻</rdg></app></l><l>自身自所尊</l>
<lb n="0314b05"/><l>真言字相應</l><l>隨力而念誦</l>
<lb n="0314b06"/><l>如聲色相應</l><l>以字為花鬘</l>
<lb n="0314b07"/><l>智者應思惟</l><l>依瑜伽相應</l>
<lb n="0314b08"/><l>於聲我今說</l><l>一<note n="0314016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">切＝字【三】</note><note n="0314016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">切＝字【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0314016"><lem>切</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">字</rdg></app>最勝成</l>
<lb n="0314b09"/><l>如來蓮華部</l><l>商佉聲念誦</l>
<lb n="0314b10"/><l>我讚如雷聲</l><l>分明稱吽字</l>
<lb n="0314b11"/><l>我說金剛部</l></lg>
<lb n="0314b12"/><p><note n="0314017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亦通乃至念誦四百三十八字宋元明甲四本俱作五言偈文八十一句</note>亦通<note n="0314018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摩醯首羅＝大自在【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩醯首羅＝大自在【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314018"><lem>摩醯首羅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">大自在</rdg></app>。念誦者成就南摩尼羯磨。
<lb n="0314b13"/>此部<note n="0314019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（作）＋念【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（作）＋念【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314019"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">作念</rdg></app>誦。如鈴鐸聲。<note n="0314020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＋（擊）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如＋（擊）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314020"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">如擊</rdg></app>箜篌<note n="0314021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聲〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0314021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔聲〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0314021"><lem>聲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>笛聲。如
<lb n="0314b14"/>舞動瓔<note n="0314022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔珞〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔珞〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314022"><lem>珞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>聲。其<app type="＊" source="0314021"><lem>聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>如孔雀鳴。如<note n="0314023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一切＝諸【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一切＝諸【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314023"><lem>一切</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">諸</rdg></app>部法
<lb n="0314b15"/>中。相應一切義。成如是音聲。而<note n="0314024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">作＋（於）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">作＋（於）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314024"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">作於</rdg></app>念誦。與
<lb n="0314b16"/>真言相應。真言者隨聲。應思惟其義。不久當
<lb n="0314b17"/>成就。此通一切部<note n="0314025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔此〕－【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0314025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔此〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0314025"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>是聲念誦儀<note n="0314026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軌＝二軌竟【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">軌＝二軌竟【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314026"><lem>軌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">二軌竟</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0314b18"/><p>我說色念誦。我今說一切。色者說為印。與此
<lb n="0314b19"/>相應轉<note place="inline"><note n="0314027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謂＝詣【明】</note><app n="0314027"><lem>謂</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">詣</rdg></app>運為也</note>善思惟其明。當安<note n="0314028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝於【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＝於【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314028"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">於</rdg></app>胸臆。印焰
<lb n="0314b20"/>明觀察。身中出金剛。甘露而灌灑。令本天喜
<lb n="0314b21"/>悅。得隱自身形。大勤勇我說。<note n="0314029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔色念誦〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔色念誦〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314029"><lem>色念誦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>由此
<lb n="0314b22"/>真言者。知以印令<note n="0314030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">成就＝我【三】，成【甲】</note><note n="0314030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">成就＝我【宋】【元】【明】，＝成【甲】</note><app n="0314030"><lem>成就</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">我</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app>。不久易餘身。<note n="0314031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＋（今）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我＋（今）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314031"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">我今</rdg></app>說
<lb n="0314b23"/>瑜伽。念誦如昔<note n="0314032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔所〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔所〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314032"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>說。其明應思惟。安置於
<lb n="0314b24"/>自處。供養以如教。純相應念誦離心喉頂舌
<lb n="0314b25"/>鼻<note n="0314033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03710;＝及與齶處【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03710;＝及與齶處【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314033"><lem>&CB03710;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">及與齶處</rdg></app>及離念內外。唯法相應<note n="0314034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耳＝爾【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耳＝爾【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314034"><lem>耳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">爾</rdg></app>。不應依於
<lb n="0314b26"/>聲。此名為金剛。瑜伽念誦儀。若知真實體。應
<lb n="0314b27"/>當知成就。而獲得常&M010527;。以此瑜伽法。相應而
<lb n="0314b28"/>住之。以菩提勝心。為成就不久。皆<note n="0314035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝悉【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＝悉【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314035"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">悉</rdg></app>得如
<lb n="0314b29"/>意。其中字念誦。如獲我今說。如是積資糧。真
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0955.0314c" n="0314c"/>
<lb n="0314c01"/>言應誦持。以文字為色。應分別觀之。作念誦
<lb n="0314c02"/>事業。月行列意生。明字與之俱。安本尊胸臆。
<lb n="0314c03"/>不久得<note n="0314036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">安怛陀娜＝道成【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">安怛陀娜＝道成【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314036"><lem>安怛陀娜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">道成</rdg></app>。於月以月合。於一切字
<lb n="0314c04"/>色。應於上思惟。光明輪莊嚴。行列不間斷。如
<lb n="0314c05"/>以線穿珠。金色以為光。晃曜本尊身。如彼彼
<lb n="0314c06"/>月字。殊勝妙真言。以成真言者。則彼彼喜悅。
<lb n="0314c07"/>力命增<note n="0314037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔益更〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔益更〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314037"><lem>益更</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>熾盛。意光明相應。我說為文
<lb n="0314c08"/>字。行列之念誦。我今<note n="0314038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遍＝通【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遍＝通【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314038"><lem>遍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">通</rdg></app>諸儀則成就物光
<lb n="0314c09"/><note n="0314039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">暉＝澤【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">暉＝澤【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314039"><lem>暉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">澤</rdg></app>。我今說。誦明念誦者。若作彼以光明成
<lb n="0314c10"/>就於諸物。應生念誦相應儀。一切真言皆得
<lb n="0314c11"/>成。一儀與相應。應作識清淨。清淨為心識。智
<lb n="0314c12"/>者然當入成就。以身以語以意。依如是物而
<lb n="0314c13"/>住。應知<note n="0314040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">四＝內【宋】【明】</note><app n="0314040"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">內</rdg></app>支<note n="0314041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＋（於）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法＋（於）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314041"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">法於</rdg></app>。瑜伽法成就。此中說為意。
<lb n="0314c14"/>獲通及地等。以身現諸身<note place="inline">決云謂隨眾生意所樂者</note></p>
<lb n="0314c15"/><p>以語<note n="0314042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辯＝辨【甲】</note><app n="0314042"><lem>辯</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">辨</rdg></app>一切。&CB00195;焰等成就。我說物成就。於
<lb n="0314c16"/><note n="0314043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（身）＋中【三】</note><note n="0314043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（身）＋中【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0314043"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">身中</rdg></app>身成就者。種類有多種。四印及餘輪壇。
<lb n="0314c17"/>瑜伽者應當盡<note n="0314044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其所＝可【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其所＝可【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314044"><lem>其所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">可</rdg></app>解者而作大曼<note n="0314045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">荼＝茶【明】＊</note><app n="0314045"><lem>荼</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">茶</rdg></app>羅。
<lb n="0314c18"/>曼荼羅儀軌成<note n="0314046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">辦＝辨【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辦＝辨【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314046"><lem>辦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">辨</rdg></app>中央三昧形。應安軟坐<note place="inline">西方
<lb n="0314c19"/>或以赤&CB00538;皮中安氈花而坐</note></p>
<lb n="0314c20"/><p>而安坐。一切瑜伽三摩地相應晝夜等至<note place="inline">謂入定也</note>
<lb n="0314c21"/><note n="0314047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔真言者住與慧念〕－【甲】</note><app n="0314047"><lem>真言者住與慧念</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>相應。中夜或明相現時。
<lb n="0314c22"/><note n="0314048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔或三更或明相〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0314048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔或三更或明相〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0314048"><lem>或三更或明相</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>決定當成就。或地及神通成
<lb n="0314c23"/>就。如來說。我今說意成就。現身而獲之。以
<lb n="0314c24"/><app type="＊" source="0314025"><lem>此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>印加持身。我今為大印。應作<note n="0314049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0314049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0314049"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>思惟。於
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0955.0315a" n="0315a"/>
<lb n="0315a01"/>成就及曼<app type="＊" source="0314045"><lem>荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">茶</rdg></app>羅念誦者。淨心則成就。我說成
<lb n="0315a02"/>就相。口身或出光明暖<note n="0315001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00195;＝焰【三】</note><note n="0315001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00195;＝焰【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0315001"><lem>&CB00195;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">焰</rdg></app>及增等。若見<note n="0315002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">昇＝升【三】</note><note n="0315002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">昇＝升【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0315002"><lem>昇</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">升</rdg></app>
<lb n="0315a03"/>空去。成就相應知於身成就。我廣說已</p>
<lb n="0315a04"/><p>我說語成就法。如獲次第說。應為先行法已。
<lb n="0315a05"/>如前法應作<note place="inline">謂自建立已來乃至大印等</note>口心印上住蓮華。應
<lb n="0315a06"/>知於心間於上住商佉<note place="inline">謂在<note n="0315003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（蓮）＋花【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（蓮）＋花【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315003"><lem>花</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">蓮花</rdg></app>上也</note>商佉中出聲。相
<lb n="0315a07"/>續無間斷。於蓮華中發生金剛舌。以白色<note place="inline">謂作赤色
<lb n="0315a08"/>上有金剛</note>舌上或想佛或寶或蓮華或羯磨金剛或
<lb n="0315a09"/>餘部印契。或一月及兩月三四及五月乃至
<lb n="0315a10"/>八箇月觀想。於此壇結<note n="0315004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">加＝跏【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315004"><lem>加</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">跏</rdg></app>趺坐。常以本寂靜
<lb n="0315a11"/>相應。分明觀商佉聲已。即依蓮華界。從花&CB00610;
<lb n="0315a12"/>出聲量如微塵。其聲出至咽。<note n="0315005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次＋（又）【三】</note><note n="0315005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次＋（又）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0315005"><lem>次</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">次又</rdg></app>至於舌。便
<lb n="0315a13"/>即成其字。舌字出光焰。<note n="0315006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">焰＝熾【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">焰＝熾【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315006"><lem>焰</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">熾</rdg></app>猛而普遍。以聲
<lb n="0315a14"/>滿虛空。行者<note n="0315007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">徑＝住【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">徑＝住【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315007"><lem>徑</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>定誦或一日及一夜。中夜或
<lb n="0315a15"/>後夜。從舌出光明。其光有大聲。或從心從脣
<lb n="0315a16"/>及齒。出間錯光明。若見如是者當知得悉地。
<lb n="0315a17"/>以此語相<note n="0315008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">應＋（成就）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">應＋（成就）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315008"><lem>應</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">應成就</rdg></app>能摧諸異宗令他發淨信。能為
<lb n="0315a18"/>眾生利益。如是瑜伽相應念誦。有比丘&CB00085;迦
<lb n="0315a19"/>者吒。<note n="0315009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔當〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔當〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315009"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得口成就。於間錯<note n="0315010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">出＝山中【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">出＝山中【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315010"><lem>出</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">山中</rdg></app>。七日而成語
<lb n="0315a20"/>成就儀則</p>
<lb n="0315a21"/><p>我今說物成就。如前瑜伽應成就。應取餘部
<lb n="0315a22"/>物等或用餘部印及真言三簸<note n="0315011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＝哆【明】</note><app n="0315011"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">哆</rdg></app><note place="inline">謂以杓應<note n="0315012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩＝娑【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">薩＝娑【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315012"><lem>薩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">娑</rdg></app><note n="0315013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00085;＋（二合訶聲）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00085;＋（二合訶聲）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315013"><lem>&CB00085;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00085;二合訶聲</rdg></app><note n="0315014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝住【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0315014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拄＝住【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0315014"><lem>拄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>物便
<lb n="0315a23"/>瀉爐中及餘聲未盡還<app type="＊" source="0315014"><lem>拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">住</rdg></app>物</note>行相作已。智者於此曼<app type="＊" source="0314045"><lem>荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">茶</rdg></app>羅。即
<lb n="0315a24"/>入羯磨三昧耶。自為一切羯磨。自在其中為
<lb n="0315a25"/>色相。一切於本部主。應與於右手印物為次
<lb n="0315a26"/>第。於金剛縛中安<note n="0315015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">物＋（物）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">物＋（物）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315015"><lem>物</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">物物</rdg></app>。類於中積。縛印當臍
<lb n="0315a27"/>下或當心。二手以縛物獻安自心。自明。智者
<lb n="0315a28"/>以此法。觀身火光聚。以先所集身口意善資
<lb n="0315a29"/>糧用以此身物。安於明手中。真言字火焰聲
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0955.0315b" n="0315b"/>
<lb n="0315b01"/>念誦。真言者盡其夜應作。不應破其坐。以此
<lb n="0315b02"/>儀則法。初夜當生暖。&CB00195;當於中夜。光焰於明
<lb n="0315b03"/>相。如是漸次加。如光焰成物。得飛騰虛空。於
<lb n="0315b04"/>三界自在。我說安<note n="0315016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＝繕【明】</note><app n="0315016"><lem>善</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">繕</rdg></app>那法。我曾已先說。應
<lb n="0315b05"/>斷一切取。應依於本明。乃至自身體。語心亦
<lb n="0315b06"/>如是。以自真言。應隱沒作本明主。應作念誦。
<lb n="0315b07"/>大金剛名者。以金剛<note n="0315017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＋（大）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大＋（大）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315017"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">大大</rdg></app>身。智者應堅住召
<lb n="0315b08"/>入縛令喜。當安於心。如自心所樂。我明觀自
<lb n="0315b09"/>身。我是虛空。由此相應成<note n="0315018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">就＋（故）【甲】</note><app n="0315018"><lem>就</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">就故</rdg></app>。乃至一切欲
<lb n="0315b10"/>界主。彼等不見形。剎那至梵天。以盡彼法作
<lb n="0315b11"/>鉤召。應作四印曼<app type="＊" source="0314045"><lem>荼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">茶</rdg></app>羅。應安意在左手。自
<lb n="0315b12"/>身安於彼。以拳應堅持。作拳為虛空。如是安
<lb n="0315b13"/>怛陀<app type="＊" source="0313011"><lem>娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">那</rdg></app>。雖忉利天宮亦不能見。遊於他化自
<lb n="0315b14"/>在<note n="0315019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（天）＋宮【三】</note><note n="0315019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（天）＋宮【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0315019"><lem>宮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">天宮</rdg></app>。恣意安樂自在乃至意所樂。丸藥口安
<lb n="0315b15"/>怛陀<app type="＊" source="0313011"><lem>娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">那</rdg></app>法</p>
<lb n="0315b16"/><p>我今略說成就法。如是觀自明。我是一切體
<lb n="0315b17"/><note place="inline">所謂以虛空內<note n="0315020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有所＝所有【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有所＝所有【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315020"><lem>有所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">所有</rdg></app>為一<note n="0315021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">體也＝切體【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">體也＝切體【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315021"><lem>體也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">切體</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0315b18"/>自身同彼印。住微細金剛三昧。入於自明心。
<lb n="0315b19"/>於丸藥成就。觀丸藥置於口。能遊須彌頂。一
<lb n="0315b20"/>切世<note n="0315022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔間〕－【甲】</note><app n="0315022"><lem>間</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不能見。藥色成大<note n="0315023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">力＝人【三】</note><note n="0315023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">力＝人【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0315023"><lem>力</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app><note place="inline">謂體隨意變身<note n="0315024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔也〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315024"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0315b21"/>受忉利天宮<note n="0315025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慾＝欲【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慾＝欲【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315025"><lem>慾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">欲</rdg></app>樂隨意得快樂。餘世間相雜。
<lb n="0315b22"/>我今說安<note n="0315026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔怛〕－【宋】【元】【甲】</note><app n="0315026"><lem>怛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>陀<app type="＊" source="0313011"><lem>娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">那</rdg></app>。丸藥依本教成。真言智
<lb n="0315b23"/>應作自明。智身前求。成就者應獻。無垢如虛
<lb n="0315b24"/>空。明身物及色。以明字行列。光焰相應住。當
<lb n="0315b25"/>入本尊身。如隱沒<note n="0315027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">住＝注【甲】</note><app n="0315027"><lem>住</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">注</rdg></app>意。從明口流出。真言
<lb n="0315b26"/>光威猛。丸藥善應成。<note n="0315028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00195;＝焰【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00195;＝焰【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315028"><lem>&CB00195;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">焰</rdg></app>氣騰生已。禁止已
<lb n="0315b27"/>安口。為不現形中自在。<note n="0315029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遊＋（戲）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遊＋（戲）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315029"><lem>遊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">遊戲</rdg></app>於四洲。剎那諸
<lb n="0315b28"/>世界。還來歸本處。所去得隨意。種種成就。藥
<lb n="0315b29"/>叉眾常以為眷屬。亦能遊戲須彌四天王下
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0955.0315c" n="0315c"/>
<lb n="0315c01"/>層四藥叉世界作無量有情利益。失正<note n="0315030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔道〕－【甲】</note><app n="0315030"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>漂
<lb n="0315c02"/>曠野<note n="0315031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賊王＝王賊【三】</note><note n="0315031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賊王＝王賊【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0315031"><lem>賊王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">王賊</rdg></app>水火等逼。起<app type="＊" source="0314049"><lem>是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>悲<note n="0315032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">憫＝愍【三】</note><note n="0315032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">憫＝愍【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0315032"><lem>憫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">愍</rdg></app>心<note n="0315033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0315033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔於〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0315033"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一
<lb n="0315c03"/>切繫縛處。我當成就已皆令得解脫</p>
<lb n="0315c04"/><p>我今已略說。廣法如大經。應觀自心<note n="0315034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">月＝日【三】</note><note n="0315034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月＝日【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0315034"><lem>月</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">日</rdg></app>。月
<lb n="0315c05"/>形<note n="0315035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＝見【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">具＝見【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315035"><lem>具</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">見</rdg></app>光明。則<app type="＊" source="0315033"><lem>於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>此月中。一字如金色。難&CB00418;
<lb n="0315c06"/>如日輪。光明普舒遍。瑜岐想光明。則其字為
<lb n="0315c07"/>輪。其輪為轉輪。持妙色形七寶圍遶。遍身毛
<lb n="0315c08"/>孔中。流出無量佛。瑜岐應思惟。用金剛界印。
<lb n="0315c09"/>四處誦真言加持。勤勇力成就。念定勤為薪。
<lb n="0315c10"/>焚燒一切罪。以真言色火。當離<note n="0315036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">疑＝言【甲】</note><app n="0315036"><lem>疑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">言</rdg></app>分別。求
<lb n="0315c11"/><note n="0315037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＋（乘）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大＋（乘）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315037"><lem>大</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">大乘</rdg></app>樂棄<note n="0315038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">小＋（乘）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0315038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">小＋（乘）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0315038"><lem>小</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">小乘</rdg></app><note n="0315039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔樂〕－【甲】</note><app n="0315039"><lem>樂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。慇懃慧菩提。住真言儀則</p>
<lb n="0315c12"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><app type="＊" source="0313007"><lem>一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">瑜伽翳迦訖沙囉烏瑟尼沙斫訖囉真言安怛陀那儀則一</rdg></app>字頂輪王瑜伽<note n="0315040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">觀行儀軌＝經【三】，究竟儀則【甲】</note><note n="0315040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">觀行儀軌＝經【宋】【元】【明】，＝究竟儀則【甲】</note><app n="0315040"><lem>觀行儀軌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">經</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">究竟儀則</rdg></app>一卷</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>